
Overview of noun modality

The noun modality has 4 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                     
1. modality, mode -- (a classification of propositions on the basis of whether they claim necessity or possibility or impossibility)
2. mood, mode, modality -- (verb inflections that express how the action or state is conceived by the speaker)
3. modality, sense modality, sensory system -- (a particular sense)
4. modality -- (a method of therapy that involves physical or electrical therapeutic treatment)
